short_description: little pop up studios is a photographer/photographic studio based in united kingdom.
long_description: when booking with me and the little pop-up studio, you are not only guaranteed beautiful and wholesome gallery of images, but also a fun and wholesome experience for you and your family. "every white wall has a story". for the lucky few of us, this comfort starts at home, surrounded by the people we love. i provide an in-home studio and on location photography experience, where families can focus on just being themselves. the results are a combination of gently posed and documentary style photos and a gallery filled with an array of emotions and expressions. let's start your journey to timeless photographs today. get to know me: meet the photographer. studio feels in the heart of your home & heart felt moments in your favourite places with your family. there's nothing i love more than capturing a growing family's unique story through my lens. my aim is to take the pressure off new, growing and busy families by simply bringing the studio to you.
